    "description": "【荒野军团】整装待发！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >割草版荒野求生！拾取多种武器，与来自四面八方的怪物进行战斗！收集物资和金币，获取超多武器、装备和法术，叠加不同功能的Buff，让自己愈战愈勇！还可以自定义游戏时长，无限制收集武器装备，任意建造自己的炮塔！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/8d26bfdca5d7245addfd1cc29d7a4b2b.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0e8a2f308122210141e3bd79d77bf7b2.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0e8a2f308122210141e3bd79d77bf7b2.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0e8a2f308122210141e3bd79d77bf7b2.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>收集</strong>木头，<strong>制造</strong>手雷和炸弹，轰炸敌人！还可以<strong>修建炮塔</strong>并不断<strong>升级</strong>强化，组成无敌的阵地，稳守其中，和Boss决一死战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/fc05de22bebfb06a87c5cb8987fe276b.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/afa71b0f2a0609fddb553169d04e146a.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/afa71b0f2a0609fddb553169d04e146a.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/afa71b0f2a0609fddb553169d04e146a.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打败敌人获取金币！<strong>金币 = 经验值</strong>，时也可用于购买/升级武器。<strong>同时装备上几十种武器</strong>——近战、远程和法术，再搭配数十种装备和Buff。<br>满级武器 + 组合 BUFF =【S 级】攻击！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/cb490f7a672021b958c7d03a0e53a2c4.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>白天</strong>适合稳打稳扎收集资源：白天可收集的资源更多，同时敌人只会攻击角色本身。<br><strong>夜间</strong>怪物出没——保护好你的<strong>月亮塔</strong>：当晚上月亮塔升起时，敌人会群起而攻之。你需要在月亮塔周围<strong>打造防线</strong>！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/e8501d8a63d872384aac04e932d949cf.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>将迷路的动物带到传送点</strong>，帮助他们逃避恶魔的入侵！作为回报，他们会赋予你特殊效果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/2a12592007bf1d979fc235a042007b85.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/5815e19a43a9d3ff2ee4b13b2b15c5c1.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/5815e19a43a9d3ff2ee4b13b2b15c5c1.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/5815e19a43a9d3ff2ee4b13b2b15c5c1.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打败首领和精英可以获取宝石。宝石可用于<strong>数值提升</strong>，以及<strong>新炮塔的解锁</strong>。<br><br><u>《荒野军团》从《土豆兄弟》、《通神榜》、《饥荒》等游戏中获得了很多灵感。 如果你喜欢我们的作品，请将游戏加入愿望单！</u><br><br>加入我们的玩家群——你们的反馈会帮助我们把游戏变得更好！<br>蓝速游戏玩家群：<strong>836595365</strong><br><br>*《荒野军团》是 Erabit Bud Scheme 的游戏之一，Bud Scheme致力于支持独立开发者/小型开发团队，落地游戏创意。<br>",
